featuresTraits:
Hobbit Resilience: Advantage on saving throws against being frightened.
Hobbit Nimbleness: Can move through the space of any creature larger than yours.
Brave Little Souls: Once per long rest, reroll a failed attack, check, or save.

--- CALLING: Storykeeper (Lore-Warden) ---
Storykeepers are the memory of the Hobbits, preserving tales of old, composing new songs, and reminding everyone of the great deeds and funny foibles of their ancestors.

--- Learned Calling Abilities ---
- Inspiring Tale: As an action, tell a brief, stirring tale. One ally within 30ft who can hear you gains temporary Fortitude equal to your Charm modifier (min 1) for 10 minutes.
- Ballad of Bravery: Once per long rest, as an action, you can sing a ballad. Choose up to two allies within 30ft. They gain advantage on their next saving throw against being frightened made within the next minute.
